{"tid":339591,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[python] 點樣save return value in recursion","createTime":"2017-07-29T07:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T04:47:31.000Z","uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97b90f02572c3f60f5d168908cd4c27701b012d6","tid":339591,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"假設有個list =[[1,'a',['cat'],2],[[[3]],'dog'],4,5]<br />\n目標係想remove all list inside the outermost list<br />\nanswer=[1,'a','cat',2,3,'dog',4,5]<br />\n於是用recursion 去solve 問題<br />\n下邊網址store 左個code<br />\n<a href=\"https://repl.it/Jnqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJnqg&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c485056e\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/Jnqg</a><br />\n<br />\n個問題係去到[cat]就quit 左 個function<br />\n求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77b62ee1fd355fee88eaad5bf210ca0ebe135d9","tid":339591,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"1. 用char做variable name係好誤導，alist入面乜都有，唔一定係char/str，應該叫item<br />\n2. 又global又local， l=[] 呢句應該放左function開頭，唔係function外"},{"pid":"e8f29821072e3ff11f6340cea171e5feaced994a","tid":339591,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"3. 第4行唔應該直接return，你應該用l+=flatten(item)將個臨時result儲落l度，最後先直接return"},{"pid":"3531905830c5648f49348eb8ebcaf864833cbfa7","tid":339591,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3. 第4行唔應該直接return，你應該用l+=flatten(item)將個臨時result儲落l度，最後先直接return</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒<br />\n一陣再試下先"},{"pid":"fd313be83381adbb5f43feffca7691f30e2f3725","tid":339591,"uid":122576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"最簡單就應該係一個一個array traverse然後concat所有array content最後reverse個array就搞掂"},{"pid":"36f5f90e63bd84b5f32e28ef6659d6343d09405c","tid":339591,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最簡單就應該係一個一個array traverse然後concat所有array content最後reverse個array就搞掂</blockquote><br />\n即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為怕行完晒個list之前return左<br />\n所以係function入邊寫多個function<br />\n會唔會好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://repl.it/JoDN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJoDN&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4119a85a\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/JoDN</a>"},{"pid":"f1322f7b33eb53f22331da9e38998b468928962f","tid":339591,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最簡單就應該係一個一個array traverse然後concat所有array content最後reverse個array就搞掂</blockquote><br />\n即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為怕行完晒個list之前return左<br />\n所以係function入邊寫多個function<br />\n會唔會好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://repl.it/JoDN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJoDN&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4119a85a\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/JoDN</a></blockquote><br />\n即係確保line 9行完晒<br />\n跟住再return"},{"pid":"a87c30591098f66b5d036a75e3eb497c595e1887","tid":339591,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FFLkuB1yp&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0315bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp</a>"},{"pid":"b002fb96b3ed861e38d017b795682be9797a5205","tid":339591,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T14:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FFLkuB1yp&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0315bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp</a></blockquote><br />\n用divide-and-conquer諗，假設我想將一個好複雜嘅list轉做1d list，<br />\n我需要design 一個function flatten(aList: list) --&gt; list<br />\n<br />\n響個function入面，首先iterate每個element，check佢係咪一個list，<br />\n     1. 係的話我要利用返flatten呢個function，將呢個element轉做1d list<br />\n     2. 唔係的話就唔需要flatten<br />\n但無論係邊個case都好，我最後都要將d element砌返做一條1d list，以滿足output嘅datatype，所以<br />\ncase 1要利用result.extend(flatten左嘅element)，將佢拼落result<br />\ncase 2就要利用result.append(element)，直接將個element砌落去result<br />\n<br />\n響呢到case 1無用到append因為一個list append另一個list會出左一個list of list，<br />\n姐係<br />\nl1 = ['a', 'b', 'c']<br />\nl2 = ['d', 'e', 'f']<br />\nl1.append(l2)會變左['a', 'b', 'c', ['d', 'e', 'f']]<br />\n所以唯有用extend，但extend嘅time complexity係O(n+k)，成個function嘅time complexity 會變左O(n^2) 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.python.org/moin/TimeComplexity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.python.org%2Fmoin%2FTimeComplexity&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2c6d9d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.python.org/moin/TimeComplexity</a>"},{"pid":"9577c808170ea887ac38a8c61346cc9beb6f6a50","tid":339591,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最簡單就應該係一個一個array traverse然後concat所有array content最後reverse個array就搞掂</blockquote><br />\nPython implements lists as arrays.  This is very inefficient."},{"pid":"1b498c7e5f62e68b1869293c7d014b64dc1b68b9","tid":339591,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FqPtfSACX&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2028f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX</a>"},{"pid":"826facd5b376e25c903bf538f514e6f9663fca6d","tid":339591,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FqPtfSACX&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2028f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX</a></blockquote><br />\nnested function <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都諗唔到幾時要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15adde638e79e484e891036abd2d2858dda55eaa","tid":339591,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FqPtfSACX&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2028f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX</a></blockquote><br />\nnested function <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都諗唔到幾時要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入面個function淨係得個outer function會重覆用咪會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過未必會醒起咁做"},{"pid":"0dd12f80a6500d3cf9777e80125ddfba534addb5","tid":339591,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FFLkuB1yp&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0315bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp</a></blockquote><br />\n用divide-and-conquer諗，假設我想將一個好複雜嘅list轉做1d list，<br />\n我需要design 一個function flatten(aList: list) --&gt; list<br />\n<br />\n響個function入面，首先iterate每個element，check佢係咪一個list，<br />\n     1. 係的話我要利用返flatten呢個function，將呢個element轉做1d list<br />\n     2. 唔係的話就唔需要flatten<br />\n但無論係邊個case都好，我最後都要將d element砌返做一條1d list，以滿足output嘅datatype，所以<br />\ncase 1要利用result.extend(flatten左嘅element)，將佢拼落result<br />\ncase 2就要利用result.append(element)，直接將個element砌落去result<br />\n<br />\n響呢到case 1無用到append因為一個list append另一個list會出左一個list of list，<br />\n姐係<br />\nl1 = ['a', 'b', 'c']<br />\nl2 = ['d', 'e', 'f']<br />\nl1.append(l2)會變左['a', 'b', 'c', ['d', 'e', 'f']]<br />\n所以唯有用extend，但extend嘅time complexity係O(n+k)，成個function嘅time complexity 會變左O(n^2) 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.python.org/moin/TimeComplexity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.python.org%2Fmoin%2FTimeComplexity&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2c6d9d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.python.org/moin/TimeComplexity</a></blockquote><br />\n你意思係[1,a]之後 睇[cat]<br />\n因為[cat]係list 要再run一次function<br />\n把cat append 落empty list/ result 到<br />\nreturn 出黎會變番[cat]<br />\n所以要用extend令[1,a]同[cat]變成[1,a,cat]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18213d67e9337a75e6e905f0c300932e18e6f885","tid":339591,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FqPtfSACX&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2028f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX</a></blockquote><br />\nnested function <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都諗唔到幾時要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入面個function淨係得個outer function會重覆用咪會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過未必會醒起咁做</blockquote><br />\nnested function好處係唔係簡潔同難D寫錯<br />\nrecursion先後次序同幾時return都要好小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e7166a8d66e5546029c08cb67a7cd7288cd20e","tid":339591,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FqPtfSACX&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2028f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX</a></blockquote><br />\nnested function <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都諗唔到幾時要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔用nested function都得。我用nested fuction嚟收埋flatten_helper。另一個做法可以係用__flatten_helper做名。不過 __係convention only。"},{"pid":"90b46e48926e67a82d6501a7cfe29b15c8ba8cbe","tid":339591,"uid":6801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FqPtfSACX&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c2028f1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/qPtfSACX</a></blockquote><br />\nnested function <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來都諗唔到幾時要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入面個function淨係得個outer function會重覆用咪會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過未必會醒起咁做</blockquote><br />\nnested function好處係唔係簡潔同難D寫錯<br />\nrecursion先後次序同幾時return都要好小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnested function好處應該係你唔會驚有人誤用你個function<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為出面call唔到"},{"pid":"cbef2da6d25eb6afc551de4a7aa7c9496d2b9add","tid":339591,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://repl.it/Jp9o/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJp9o%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=67b50ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/Jp9o/0</a><br />\n傻瓜版方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf574be12f84ae901d43dba055ad8743b808e5c","tid":339591,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://repl.it/Jp9o/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJp9o%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=67b50ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/Jp9o/0</a><br />\n傻瓜版方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWhat happens if there is a '[' inside your string data?"},{"pid":"07e1a80adb3ad590b9aaf8711e6f93484464f8bf","tid":339591,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://repl.it/Jp9o/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJp9o%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=67b50ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/Jp9o/0</a><br />\n傻瓜版方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWhat happens if there is a '[' inside your string data?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nString type number, e.g.  '0', '1'... &amp; '['  ']' = Bugs<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508ecda6eda23bd381bbaec3691db680453b724d","tid":339591,"uid":123988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FFLkuB1yp&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0315bb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/FLkuB1yp</a></blockquote><br />\n用divide-and-conquer諗，假設我想將一個好複雜嘅list轉做1d list，<br />\n我需要design 一個function flatten(aList: list) --&gt; list<br />\n<br />\n響個function入面，首先iterate每個element，check佢係咪一個list，<br />\n     1. 係的話我要利用返flatten呢個function，將呢個element轉做1d list<br />\n     2. 唔係的話就唔需要flatten<br />\n但無論係邊個case都好，我最後都要將d element砌返做一條1d list，以滿足output嘅datatype，所以<br />\ncase 1要利用result.extend(flatten左嘅element)，將佢拼落result<br />\ncase 2就要利用result.append(element)，直接將個element砌落去result<br />\n<br />\n響呢到case 1無用到append因為一個list append另一個list會出左一個list of list，<br />\n姐係<br />\nl1 = ['a', 'b', 'c']<br />\nl2 = ['d', 'e', 'f']<br />\nl1.append(l2)會變左['a', 'b', 'c', ['d', 'e', 'f']]<br />\n所以唯有用extend，但extend嘅time complexity係O(n+k)，成個function嘅time complexity 會變左O(n^2) 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.python.org/moin/TimeComplexity\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.python.org%2Fmoin%2FTimeComplexity&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2c6d9d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.python.org/moin/TimeComplexity</a></blockquote><br />\n你意思係[1,a]之後 睇[cat]<br />\n因為[cat]係list 要再run一次function<br />\n把cat append 落empty list/ result 到<br />\nreturn 出黎會變番[cat]<br />\n所以要用extend令[1,a]同[cat]變成[1,a,cat]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  神啊 , 請受小弟一拜"},{"pid":"5e0dfe6496b00527303c9fb2f92d83825c9c0072","tid":339591,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://repl.it/Jxz7/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJxz7%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=914a7bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/Jxz7/0</a>"},{"pid":"3aac63cf919ba655ef94f0d119a31388c566e208","tid":339591,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://repl.it/Jxz7/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJxz7%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=914a7bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/Jxz7/0</a></blockquote><br />\nthe previous solution isn't quite pure recursive. (since there is a for loop.)"},{"pid":"e00d0f509133172808d024568cf5bd1877e8a1e0","tid":339591,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"another cooler solution with reduce:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://repl.it/JyBM/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJyBM%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a81a20fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/JyBM/0</a>"},{"pid":"8a7870c6b7a6f161f731914128790623a4deed95","tid":339591,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>another cooler solution with reduce:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://repl.it/JyBM/0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frepl.it%2FJyBM%2F0&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a81a20fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://repl.it/JyBM/0</a></blockquote><br />\neverything is reduce afterall"}]}